  "prompt": "What would be the Wipro joining dates for campus placed 2017 batch?",
  "response": "The exact joining dates for campus-placed students can be variable and depend on several factors including company policy, project requirements, or training schedules. Typically, for the 2017 batch, the joining dates for Wipro might range from mid-2017 to early 2018. Many IT companies like Wipro often issue joining dates after completing necessary background checks, training, or depending on the needs of specific projects.\n\nFor precise information, candidates would generally receive official communication directly from Wipro, usually through email or the company's onboarding portal. If you were one of the candidates, you should check your email or contact your campus placement cell or Wipro HR representative for detailed information.",
